vels in america and the west indies  in newton dennison mereness travels in the american colonies the macmillan company p    nicholas michael butler  votaries of apollo the st cecilia society and the patronage of concert music in charleston south carolina  univ of south carolina press p  isbn    alexia jones helsley  a guide to historic beaufort south carolina the history press p  isbn    the south carolina historical and genealogical magazine south carolina historical society  pp ra   national genealogical society quarterly the society  p    alexander samuel salley  marriage notices in the southcarolina gazette and its successors  j munsells sons pp –   richard henry greene ed  the new york genealogical and biographical record henry reed stiles melatiah everett dwight george austin morrison john reynolds totten hopper striker mott charles andrew ditmas harold minot pitman louis effingham de forest conklin mann arthur s maynard new york genealogical and biographical society p    maturin l delafield  william smith judge of the supreme court of the province of new york william smith  the historian chiefjustice of new york and of canada p    a b ronald roy nelson august  the home office  duke university press p  retrieved  september    notes and queries for readers and writers collectors and librarians oxford university press  p    david dobson  american data from the aberdeen journal  genealogical publishing com p  isbn  retrieved  september    the south carolina historical and genealogical magazine south carolina historical society  p    peter wilson coldham  north american wills registered in london  genealogical publishing com p  isbn   retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlejohngordonmerchantoldid categories s births deathsbusinesspeople from charleston south carolinaenglish emigrants to british north americahidden categories use american english from july all wikipedia articles written in american englishuse mdy dates from july  navigation menu personal 