 mobile to quebeck consequently he will take philadelphia in his way he has a very pretty botanical turn is very new and curious in his observation i will recommend him to your acquaintance and i am certain you will be much pleased with his he will give you a very particular account of the plants of this country i beg you will make my respectful compliments acceptable to mrs logan and that you will remember me kindly to mr pemberton i wish you many returns of the new year and am with real esteem your most obdt servt john gordon   lord adam gordon c  keith w murray ed a manuscript by lord adam gordon pdf p    lord adam gordon  journal of an officers travels in america and the west indies  in newton dennison mereness travels in the american colonies the macmillan company p    nicholas michael butler  votaries of apollo the st cecilia society and the patronage of concert music in charleston south carolina  univ of south carolina press p  isbn    alexia jones helsley  a guide to historic beaufort south carolina the history press p  isbn    the south carolina historical and genealogical magazine south carolina historical society  pp ra   national genealogical society quarterly the society  p    alexander samuel salley  marriage notices in the southcarolina gazette and its successors  j munsells sons pp –   richard henry greene ed  the new york genealogical and biographical record henry reed stiles melatiah everett dwight george austin morrison john reynolds totten hopper striker mott charles andrew ditmas harold minot pitman louis effingham de forest conklin mann arthur s maynard new york genealogical and biographical society p    maturin l delafield  william smith judge of the supreme court of the province of new york william smith  the historian chiefjustice of new york and of canada p    a b ronald roy nelson august  the home office  duke university press p  retrieved  september    notes and queries for readers and writers collectors and librarians oxford university p